==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Horning
<hw>Horn"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Appearance of the moon when
increasing, or in the form of a crescent.</def> <rj><au>J.
Gregory.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Letters of horning</b></col> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld>,
<cd>the process or authority by which a person, directed by the decree
of a court of justice to pay or perform anything, is ordered to comply
therewith.</cd> <rj><au>Mozley & W.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hornish</ent>⟦br⟧
